Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你又開始疾走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只為方南奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在回到日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最近說不定可以碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣的話 你會改變主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼改天見
