Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,END OF SUMMAR 淘汰賽決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待已久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這番對話好像最近剛講過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入總決賽的包括我們在內共有4所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了決定東日本巔峰的時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個好厚的信封袋是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進入總決賽的選手名單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.55,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,67)\c&H1112C3&\fnFZYouXian-Z09}日{\c&HB73919&}本疾走協會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.55,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,281)}上午賽事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.55,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,489)}下午賽事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.55,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,558)}計時賽會場：札幌巨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總決賽首先要進行決定分組的預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致是採用競速形式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們比賽的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮城的花京院高中？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有聽過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他們去年沒有進前八
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 連前十六強都沒有進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是新參賽的隊伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 搞不好能輕鬆獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懈怠…是最大的敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懈怠…是不能容許發生的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懈怠…是我們的強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然避免了跟之前重複
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 的確是重複了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中疾走的隊伍 可能會在一年內沒落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有可能變成難以置信的強隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點你們自己應該深有體會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 對手如何與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只要呈現自己出最棒的疾走就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是這個賽事成為了我參加疾走的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要踏上那令人憧憬的舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很晚了 我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神你們平常都跑著回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時間可不能讓女孩子一個人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你過得如何 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過得很好啊　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你換號碼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在這裡簽名　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.51,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不是從美國打來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今早回到日本了　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那你要在日本待到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近會一直待在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被仙台的高中聘請了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細情況之後再跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也轉學過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然跟我說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在現在的學校很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.76,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公交車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 之後再談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的電話是你爸爸打的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他之前都一直住在美國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在自我介紹的時候 說是住在親戚家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為媽媽在我小時候就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是爸爸他說之後會住在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那不是很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 那兩個一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們賽跑過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不算是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在途中遇到後不由得就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為這傢伙迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你擅自跟著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道你是自信滿滿地朝反方向跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這是一邊迷路一邊比賽過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就這麼無謂地消耗體力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明吃過早餐的 總覺得已經餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個油耗差的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 我做了飯團帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春之食
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生親手做的飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也請用 我做了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 但是我吃過早飯才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我真的已經吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從法蘭克福過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是班機延遲 被隊友丟下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒空吃早餐 真是狼狽不堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 難道說你是EOS的參賽者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你們也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.76,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫夏凪瞳彌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起我是花京院高校的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在方南學園也是名指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫櫻井奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的職位也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你說「從今天起」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我和我的隊友在北海道還是第一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那你要和第一次見面的人組隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我十分期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣也不炎熱 真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種來到北方的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剛剛那個可不是冷笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是總決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實有種備受矚目的高中運動的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 果然有很多高大的選手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是三年級的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個還是小孩子的體型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然身高還可以 但是不夠強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從現在起才開始發育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是從現在才要開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要面對現實啊 小日向同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我眼中可是一點雜質都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待時機成熟了就會發育成那樣的體型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時 你沉睡著的力量就會覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被激勵了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾輩聽了都有點害怕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定在這場聯賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡在小日向同學體內的巨龍將…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原來是一條沉睡的巨龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向同學 那不是李 是肯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.24,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,註：小日向把李小龍和肯尼·拉貝爾弄混了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是成龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介 不要太過鼓勵這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變得很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.50,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,李？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.03,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,成龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 他真心覺得好笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星高校最後的接棒也十分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西星的跑者 諏訪憐治選手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是表現的太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,End of Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達終點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間…出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差0.8秒就追上大賽記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5分5秒48
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想趕緊再跟那些傢伙比試一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是激動人心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次我要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有出息的一年級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面開始介紹下午即將出場的兩組隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是花京院高等學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這支隊伍今年迎來新的教練 獲得重生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有這位教練的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中疾走部不會獲得這麼大的成長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾走之父 「王者」櫻井讓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:29.92,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(385,590)}櫻井讓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到在這裡能遇上王者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得你們的姓氏一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學你也沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 爸爸從來都不會跟我說起關於工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只是稍微有點吃驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來介紹的是 一年級就被選為隊員的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.50,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(385,590)}夏凪瞳彌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夏凪同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.71,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(1020,579)}維田天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此 他們能有這麼多的介紹時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明他們是十分備受矚目的高校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把之前的隊伍解散 再招來強勁的隊員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.40,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是兩位雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十公野哉 五十公野了選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.77,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(385,590)}五十公野哉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:27.27,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(998,592)}五十公野了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩位選手曾經是馬戲團的人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的體能備受矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 這位是隊長青葉選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.24,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(385,590)}青葉南平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是唯一一位原花京院疾走部的隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將如何引領全新的隊員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後介紹的是高中疾走界的希望之星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神巴選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.00,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4E9BCC&\pos(937,585)}八神巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸 你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說過他回到日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我也吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到能在這裡和巴一起比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣 恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡跑都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是為了隊伍而跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.71,newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H8C2FED&\pos(651,188)}出場順序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏凪同學 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像這樣和你們的隊伍比賽 我很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 也請你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你內心思緒萬千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的內心激盪著許多複雜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是調弦前的管絃樂隊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要按照我自己的方式去跑就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會去想巴的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想與本大爺比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這想法可是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爺可沒有競賽的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的只有一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在說你不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的目標是最快的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼很遺憾 你跑步這件事本身就毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂最快是我讓上帝那傢伙創造出來的詞彙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒一起跑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方南對你來說 會不會太屈才了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定要在方南一直跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思考並不是一件壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊伍裡的大家也跟你一樣在考慮很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你並不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾走就是這樣的一項運動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一場比賽雖說是計時賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻有本次大賽最受矚目的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聘請[國王]櫻井讓來做教練的花京院高等學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此還有[國王]的親生女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[公主]做指揮的方南學園高等學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我也認為那就是疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 音調一致了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來場精彩的比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.47,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上迎來直接對決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會多想也是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也全部都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們方南
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在把我們擁有的全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部拼上 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先飛奔而出的是方南
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是花京院八神巴選手的弟弟八神陸選手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好哦 哉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.58,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩萬分的起步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像現在這樣跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 現在可以了 往左邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不是繞了一個大圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哉 從外面過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十公野哉選手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充分發揮了自己身體能力的靈活表現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝到了八神陸選手的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.59,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的加速是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八神 後方1.2秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是1.5秒後匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺氣氛好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來 陸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向前輩 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 快沒氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 了這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在從右邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.35,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,注意右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.44,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,從左邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過只要維持住這個差距
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希斯他就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是在後半程突然加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說之前一直都是故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時拼湊的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在一口氣超過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左邊又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉前輩又追上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.72,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,青葉同學 跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是故意被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 因為今天是第一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在實戰中進行各種嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢好慢好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說沒有賽跑的意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼最快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比宇宙歷史還早一兆倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經像這樣拚命跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維田天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花京院高中最後一棒的八神巴選手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現在了開幕式現場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保持著壓倒性的領先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠遠拉開和方南學園的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能像現在這樣一起賽跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來吧 恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然以為你我是同一種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是我一直搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是恭介還是希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是巴的疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達終點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經比之前合宿時快很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這壓倒性的實力差…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的選手好像回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 瞳彌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 我得了第一名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 挺厲害麼 奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾走好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是爸爸的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 你要好好聽爺爺奶奶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸會一直和奈奈在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別走 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別扔下奈奈 別走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到再次見面竟是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉一直邀請你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不該邀請你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有恭介 希斯和我在的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為這種邂逅是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為有我們三人的疾走才是最理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就算有交集 也沒有聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直走著不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陰暗陰暗 don't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好這只是計時賽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用米做的面是麵粉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在總決賽讓我們一雪前恥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門脇說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要想一想為了獲勝必須做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後運用到下一場比賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪兒都行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有應該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.77,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巴一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是在一起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在追趕著那個背影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想追卻又追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直認為總有一天會追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果卻是無論怎麼追還是追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反 我開始覺得哥哥是不是有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論颳風下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算淋得渾身濕透也在外面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怪人才會做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開始這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸 一起去跑步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巴一起跑不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是陸你有才能 只要努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.25,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪巴 我才不開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不想再疾走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是以前也不是我自己想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 陸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸
