Comment: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,++++ STEP 09 HOME 僅存於此之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我忘飯團了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜 人家明明很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來 八神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步已經暴怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經下定決心要得到那個奢侈的飯團了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點！八神！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 疾走王子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「為了巨大飯團而奔跑」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了愛
